Package: task
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: task runner / build tool written in Go (Taskfile.dev)
 Task is a task runner and build tool that aims to be simpler and easier to
 use than GNU Make. Tasks are declared in a YAML "Taskfile.yml"; Task resolves
 their dependencies, runs the commands, and skips up-to-date work via file
 checksums or timestamps.
 .
 Foundry Linux vendors the upstream go-task release binary so the package
 resolves from apt.foundrylinux.org rather than a third-party repo.
